                          Vault of Horror
                        </em>
                         and 
                        <em>
                          From Beyond the Grave
                        </em>
                        . Perhaps they would have done better by shortening 
                        <em>
                          I, Monster
                        </em>
                         and using it in one of them instead.
                      </p>
