                      To the Devil a Daughter 
                      <span
                        class="text-sm font-light leading-none text-muted"
                      >
                        1976
                      </span>
                    </a>
                    <picture>
                      <source
                        media="(prefers-color-scheme: dark)"
                        srcset="/svg/2-stars-dark.svg"
                      />
                      <img
                        alt="D+: 2 stars (out of 5)"
                        class="mb-4"
